{"tid":1651102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊入嚟檢討下","createTime":"2019-10-13T08:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T10:10:55.000Z","uid":8141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d9a59c20c415f0f241eaba6d30ba6afe43a6e8","tid":1651102,"uid":8141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:46:38.000Z","msg":"雖然唔想承認，事實上今日開花的確開得唔理想<br />\n不過唔好散布失敗主義住先<br />\n討論下，檢討下，令運動重回正軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得有幾個原因<br />\n一：活動太密，持續咗幾個月大家都攰，係唔係集中啲一星期搞一至兩個呢？<br />\n二：和理非衝破唔到蒙面法嘅心理關口，少咗和理非掩護，勇武好多時難落手<br />\n三：連登太多失敗主義，我地係要檢討之後嘅方向，而唔係沉溺於過往嘅失敗<br />\n<br />\n明白大家好灰同覺得唔甘心，但除咗埋怨休息主義，不如諗下有咩好橋<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不割蓆唔係得個講，要做<br />\n<br />\n最後，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7cdedb2b178eafce6b161a611dd1c09b15cbdc47","tid":1651102,"uid":93383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:47:35.000Z","msg":"聽日集會同我出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d580616240b8538da6701c7fe5ddc50fdf32816","tid":1651102,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be12e672901e32dadbb982f88d1f0f00d377486a","tid":1651102,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:48:50.000Z","msg":"要救手足，呢個最關鍵&hellip;"},{"pid":"f0785897523129fc8a7a9072f1a8079059de3425","tid":1651102,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:49:07.000Z","msg":"不割蓆!不分化!"},{"pid":"bb9a14dc74785e123633eaf2c7afaaad66f5a39b","tid":1651102,"uid":34869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:49:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲叫密?</span><br />\